{"tid":202308,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大推廣文 - 你問我答 (2)","createTime":"2017-04-15T11:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T10:54:27.000Z","uid":5889,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1feb17b66394d1ee558a4212c48270bf26cee7c4","tid":202308,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:46:03.000Z","msg":"各位DSE既同學仔大家好, 唔知你地諗好入咩大學同讀咩科未呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日小妹我開呢個post就係為大家打打氣, 順便同大家介紹下科大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1. 科大名聲好, 排名高<br />\n科大, 別名<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Asia MIT, 香港第0</span></span><br />\n根據QS排名, 科大<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">曾經</span></span>超越港大成為左香港第0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科大既engine同business係17年既排名更加比港大個排名高唔少<br />\n第時入到科大比d豬朋狗友問你出路, 你都絕對可以好驕傲咁講我讀科大啊, 相信唔少人都會讀你叻仔叻女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 科大學術氣氛好<br />\n大家咁辛苦入到大學梗係想追求更多既知識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n科大係呢方面就訓練到學生十分著重讀書, 每星期都安排唔同既功課同測驗比學生溫故而知新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以見到既就係同學落堂去就擁埋去教授到問書, 問完就會去拉把溫習, 同學之間都會有各種既學術討論, 係咁既氛圍底下, 你GPA都自然會高啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 科大男女比例均衡<br />\n街外人經常流傳科大係咩少林寺啊, 格劍聖地等<br />\n呢d其實都係唔太正確既講法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以business school為例, 16intake男女比例為<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">47:53</span></span>, 53既仲要係女黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試想像下上堂acct堂, 前後左右都係女既話, 你每堂都有動力去上啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSource:<a href=\"http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fundergrad.bm.ust.hk%2Feng%2Fwhy%2Fstudents%2Four_students%2Findex.jsp&d=lEFZiSwVnaVog3Ki0s%2BD%2F%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=e4d34cd4\" target=\"_blank\">http://undergrad.bm.ust.hk/eng/why/students/our_students/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n再聽下幾個名人分享科大:<br />\n1. 嶺大分數, 三大名氣/engine就是ust(鍵盤騎士, 2015) <br />\n相信大家都聽過呢類型既說話, 想用大學黎證明自己能力, 科大絕對係你既首選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 港大張xx/鏗x都同鍵騎有唔少交情, 佢地都好支持鍵騎入讀科大civil, 認為係明智之選<br />\n<br />\n各位DSE同學仔聽完係咪心動呢, 如果係就請立即登入JUPAS Account, 更改你既選擇至JS5xxxx (任何你心儀既科大科目)<br />\n祝福你地DSE都能順利渡過, 9月係科大呢個大家庭見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64eea45363b12f168008bff41151d9ac977115b5","tid":202308,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8db8492028516a264ee7dd5915fc1d71598a95b7","tid":202308,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:55:40.000Z","msg":"亞洲MIT<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80c56cd32666d4389f081f9eb9a89ebfb1332a43","tid":202308,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:59:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f54bbea87ff317702ec6627482a39ceca6095944","tid":202308,"uid":33422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T11:59:44.000Z","msg":"至少唔會fing j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acdef59eceaa6932ef52452b3d30bc3f0e5dd69b","tid":202308,"uid":78166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:08:13.000Z","msg":"考完dse, 直入ust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4e60f993d016bb11c75e07d2314c118fe711ec","tid":202308,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T12:43:0